    <image source="/images/turt_pizza.jpeg" width="55%"/>
    <p>
      So lets condsider a slightly different relation, by putting the turtle on a diet,
      <me>
        D:Z\rightarrow F
      </me>
      defined as the following
    </p>
    <image source="/images/d.jpeg" width="100%"/>
    <p>
      Now it makes sense to use the <em>of</em> notation of functions because for example there is only one way to write the folowing:
